<div id="infobox">
  <%
    var day = barrelsPerDay
    var sec = day / (24 * 60 * 60)
    var mils = (day / 1000000).toFixed(1)
    var ones = sec.toFixed(1)
  %>
  <div class="infobox-icon">?</div>
  <div class="infobox-body infobox-hidden">
    <h2>World Crude Oil Consumption Rate</h2>

    <h4><%= mils %> million barrels per day,<br>
       <%= ones %> barrels per second,<br>
       159 litres or 42 gallons per barrel.</h4>

    <p>The falling barrels visualize the average crude oil consumption rate in 2014. The oil consumption statistics are provided by <a href="https://www.indexmundi.com/energy/?product=oil&graph=consumption&display=rank">Index Mundi</a>. Animated on <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API">canvas</a> with <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/sprinkler">Sprinkler</a>. Emoji graphics by <a href="https://openmoji.org/">OpenMoji</a>.</p>

